# ⏱️ 3. Scheduling (CRON)

You wanted:

* XML job → every **1 min**
* Retry job → every **2 mins**

---

### ✅ Scheduler

```java
@Component
@RequiredArgsConstructor
public class JobScheduler {

    private final JobLauncher jobLauncher;
    private final Job xmlJob;
    private final Job retryFailedFilesJob;

    @Scheduled(cron = "0 */1 * * * *") // every 1 min
    public void runXmlJob() throws Exception {
        jobLauncher.run(xmlJob, new JobParametersBuilder()
                .addLong("time", System.currentTimeMillis())
                .toJobParameters());
    }

    @Scheduled(cron = "0 */2 * * * *") // every 2 mins
    public void runRetryJob() throws Exception {
        jobLauncher.run(retryFailedFilesJob, new JobParametersBuilder()
                .addLong("time", System.currentTimeMillis())
                .toJobParameters());
    }
}
```

